sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Page as Listing page wrapper
  participant Hook as useModulePageLayout
  participant Public as public/configs/modulePageLayouts.json
  participant Layout as ModuleListingLayout
  participant Filters as useFilters
  participant Data as Catalog JS

  User->>Page: Open /dsa or /case-studies or /references
  Page->>Hook: moduleKey = dsa | caseStudies | references
  Hook->>Public: fetch /configs/modulePageLayouts.json
  Public-->>Hook: config section for module
  Page->>Data: import items, tags, option arrays
  Page->>Layout: config + items + optionsBySource
  Layout->>Filters: apply search, selects, tags, sort
  Filters-->>Layout: filteredItems
  Layout-->>User: paginated DisplayCard grid
